>
  <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-5">
    <p class="eh-animate text-center mx-auto" data-animation="fadeInLeft" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 37px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -1px; color: #000000; max-width: 70%;">
      "EventHex.ai revolutionized the way we managed the Gulf Indian Trade Expo. Its efficiency allowed us to focus on creating a world-class experience for our participants and exhibitors. We highly recommend EventHex.ai to anyone looking for reliable and professional event management solutions!"
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-[50px]">
      <img
        src="https://eventhex.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-503170913.svg"
        alt="Business Kerala"
        class="h-[60px] w-auto"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="https://eventhex.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Noushad-EP.jpeg"
        alt="Noushad EP"
        class="w-[80px] h-[80px] rounded-xl object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div>
        <p class="text-black font-heading text-[22px] font-medium">Noushad EP</p>
        <p class="text-eh-desc text-[16px]">Founder & Chairman, Business Kerala</p>
      </div>
    </div>
